<article>
  <div class="banner">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>聯絡城市動力</h1>
    </div>    
    </div>
    
    <div id="crumb">
        <section class="container" >
          <ol class="breadcrumb">
            <li><%= link_to "首頁", root_path %></li>
            <li>客戶服務</li>
            <li class="active">聯絡城市動力</li>
          </ol>
        </section>
    </div>
    
    <section class="contact">
    <div class="container">
    <h1>聯絡城市動力</h1>
        <div id="contact">
          <ol>
            <li>投資BES站點<br>
            投資交換機櫃，可協助您賣車，並擁有交換費用收益</li>
            <li>投資公共EBIKE 公共電動二輪車租賃系統<br>
            除了EBIKE站的租金收益，車量外型皆可置放您的廣告訊息，在您想要的區域內服務可達到最佳的宣傳效果</li>
            <li>經銷/代銷車款<br>
            <span>若您已有店面，歡迎與我們合作銷售車輛</span>
            <span>若想了解更多細節，歡迎與城市動力聯繫</span>
            </li>
          </ol>
        <%= form_for(@contact, :url => contacts_path(), html: { id: "newthiscontact",class: "form-inline", role: "form" } ) do |f| %>
        <div class="radio">
            <% @options.each_with_index do | option, index | %>
              <% if index == 0 %>
                <%= f.radio_button :subject, option[0], checked: true %>
              <% else %>
                <%= f.radio_button :subject, option[0] %>
              <% end %>
                <label for='<%= "contact_subject_#{option[0]}" %>' ><%= option[1] %> </label>
            <% end %>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-xs-6 form01">
              <div class="form-group">
                  <label for="formName">姓名</label>
                  <%= f.text_field :name, required: true, class: 'form-control required', id: 'formName' %>
              </div>
              <div class="form-group">
                  <label for="formPhone">電話</label>
                  <%= f.text_field :phone, required: true, class: 'form-control required digits', id: 'formPhone' %>
              </div>
              <div class="form-group">
                  <label for="formEmail">信箱</label>
                  <%= f.text_field :email, required: true, class: 'form-control required email', id: 'formEmail' %>
              </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-xs-6 form02">
            <%= f.text_area :content, id: "textarea", required: true, class: 'form-control', placeholder: '請輸入你的留言' %>
            <div class="code"><%= recaptcha_tags :display => { :theme => "clean" } %></div>
            <%= f.submit '送出',class: 'btn' %>
          </div>
        </div>
        <% end %>

        
        <h2>關注我們</h2>
        <div class="row link">
          <a class="col-xs-6 link01" href="https://www.facebook.com/pages/%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%8B%95%E5%8A%9BCity-power/722780041116958?fref=ts" target="_blank" >
            <h3>Facebook</h3><p>加入粉絲團，不錯過任何一則最新消息</p>   
          </a>
          <div class="col-xs-6 link02">
            <p>與城市動力成為好友，更多好康優惠與消息，即時了解</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <h2>服務中心列表</h2>
          <div class="centreList">
            <h3>中和建一店</h3><p>地址：新北市中和區建一路7號</p><span>連絡電話：02-2228-1821</span>
          </div>
          <div class="centreList">
            <h3>蘆州店</h3><p>地址：新北市蘆州區中山二路280號</p><span>連絡電話：02-2848-6381</span>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    </section>
</article>
<script src="/js/jquery.placeholder.js"></script> 
<script>$('textarea').placeholder();</script>
